Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:59.75,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)\blur3}君といると世界が違うみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:03.63,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私には無い物を持ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.92,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だからちょっとだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:09.62,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ほんの少しだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.75,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羨ましくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:15.36,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\blur3}それを持ってたらどんなに…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:24.05,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの時あげたプレゼントを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:27.96,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あんなに喜んでくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:33.54,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私も嬉しくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:39.02,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悩みも優しく止んだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:45.99,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}愛とか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:48.45,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}未来とか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:52.71,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}信じることも知らなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:55.55,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}わからないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:57.49,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}過ごしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:59.67,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}小さな光が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.88,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}今は大きくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:05.25,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}辛いとか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:07.60,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}怖いとか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:12.39,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}1人じゃ何も出来ないことも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.04,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}一緒だから強くなれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:20.44,OP_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H896FE7&}君が大丈夫にしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:59.75,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)\blur3}只要和你在一起 彷彿世界都不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:03.63,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有著我沒有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.92,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我有一些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:09.62,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有那麼一些些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.75,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:15.36,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\blur3}要是我也有該多好…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:24.05,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時我送給你禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:27.96,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒想到你會那麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:33.54,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:39.02,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煩惱也隨之消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:45.99,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}所謂的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:48.45,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}所謂的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:52.71,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}從來沒有去相信過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:55.55,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}一直沒想明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:57.49,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}就那麼虛度著光陰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:59.67,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}當時的微光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.88,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}已然填滿了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:05.25,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}有時會難受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:07.60,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}有時會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:12.39,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}有時會感到束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.04,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}兩人一起就能迎刃而解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:20.44,OP_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&H7084F5&}你就是我的強心針
